first_para: David Julian Winnick (born 26 June 1933) is a British Labour Party politician who has been the Member of Parliament (MP) for Walsall North since 1979. Previously he was the MP for Croydon South from 1966 to 1970.

full.extract:
David Julian Winnick (born 26 June 1933) is a British Labour Party politician who has been the Member of Parliament (MP) for Walsall North since 1979. Previously he was the MP for Croydon South from 1966 to 1970.
